<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Karta Postaci — Wiktoria</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;900&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Crimson+Pro:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --indigo: #3B2F6B;
    --indigo-deep: #1E1535;
    --gold: #C9A84C;
    --gold-bright: #F2C94C;
    --gold-dim: #7A6230;
    --black: #0A0712;
    --white: #F0EBE1;
    --white-dim: #9E9080;
    --red-dim: #8B3030;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background-color: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(59,47,107,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(59,47,107,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 900px; height: 900px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(59,47,107,0.4) 0%, transparent 70%);
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .scanlines {
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 4px);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 999;
  }

  .anubis-deco {
    position: fixed; right: -40px; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    opacity: 0.04; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px 80px;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }

  .header-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 6px;
    color: var(--gold-dim); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.1s;
  }

  .header-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 7vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 900; color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1; letter-spacing: 3px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.2s;
  }
  .header-title span { color: var(--gold); }

  .header-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif; font-style: italic;
    font-size: 19px; color: var(--white-dim);
    margin-top: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.35s;
  }

  .divider {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px;
    margin: 24px auto 0; max-width: 400px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.45s;
  }
  .divider-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold-dim)); }
  .divider-line.right { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold-dim), transparent); }
  .divider-symbol { color: var(--gold); font-size: 22px; }

  /* CARD */
  .card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: rgba(10,7,18,0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards;
  }
  .card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.63s; }
  .card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.76s; }
  .card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.89s; }
  .card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 1.02s; }
  .card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 1.15s; }
  .card:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 1.28s; }

  .card::before, .card::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute;
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    border-color: var(--gold); border-style: solid; opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .card::before { top: -1px; left: -1px; border-width: 2px 0 0 2px; }
  .card::after  { bottom: -1px; right: -1px; border-width: 0 2px 2px 0; }

  .card-stripe {
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), var(--gold-bright), var(--gold), transparent);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .card.booster { border-color: rgba(76,175,128,0.2); }
  .card.booster .card-stripe { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #2A6B4A, #4CAF80, #2A6B4A, transparent); }
  .card.debuff  { border-color: rgba(196,92,92,0.2); }
  .card.debuff  .card-stripe { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #6B2A2A, #C45C5C, #6B2A2A, transparent); }

  .card-inner { padding: 28px 32px 32px; }

  .card-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 5px; color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .card-label::after {
    content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.3), transparent);
  }
  .card.booster .card-label { color: #4CAF80; }
  .card.booster .card-label::after { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(76,175,128,0.3), transparent); }
  .card.debuff  .card-label { color: #C45C5C; }
  .card.debuff  .card-label::after { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(196,92,92,0.3), transparent); }

  /* AVATAR */
  .avatar-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; }

  .avatar-identity h2 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600; color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .avatar-identity .role {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gold-dim); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .avatar-identity p {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif; font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--white-dim); line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic;
  }
  .avatar-tools h3 {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--gold-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .tool-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; }
  .tool-chip {
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
    padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--white-dim);
    transition: all 0.25s ease; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .tool-chip::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: var(--gold); transform: translateX(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease; opacity: 0.08;
  }
  .tool-chip:hover { color: var(--gold); border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.6); }
  .tool-chip:hover::before { transform: translateX(0); }

  /* SKILL LIST */
  .skill-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }

  .skill-item {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 16px; align-items: start;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    transition: all 0.25s ease; cursor: default;
  }
  .skill-item:hover { background: rgba(59,47,107,0.12); }
  .skill-item:hover .skill-name { color: var(--gold-bright); }
  .card.booster .skill-item { border-left-color: rgba(76,175,128,0.15); }
  .card.booster .skill-item:hover { border-left-color: #4CAF80; background: rgba(42,107,74,0.1); }
  .card.booster .skill-item:hover .skill-name { color: #6DCFA0; }

  .skill-icon { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1; margin-top: 3px; }

  .skill-name {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 4px;
    transition: color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .card.booster .skill-name { color: #4CAF80; }

  .skill-desc {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif; font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--white-dim); line-height: 1.5; font-style: italic;
  }

  /* MISSION LOG */
  .mission-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 22px; }
  .mission-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr; gap: 14px; align-items: start; }
  .mission-num {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold-dim); margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .mission-text { font-size: 16px; color: var(--white); line-height: 1.5; }
  .mission-text strong {
    color: var(--gold-bright); font-weight: 600; display: block;
    font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .mission-note {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif; font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--white-dim); margin-top: 5px;
  }

  /* BUGS */
  .bugs-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
  .bug-item {
    border: 1px solid rgba(139,48,48,0.25);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    background: rgba(60,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .card.debuff .bug-item { border-color: rgba(196,92,92,0.2); }
  .bug-item:hover { border-color: rgba(196,92,92,0.45); background: rgba(196,92,92,0.05); }
  .bug-item:hover .bug-name { color: #C45C5C; }
  .bug-name {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--red-dim); margin-bottom: 5px;
    text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .bug-desc {
    font-size: 15px; color: var(--white-dim);
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.45;
  }

  /* ACTIVE BUILD */
  .build-box {
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
    padding: 24px; background: rgba(59,47,107,0.1);
  }
  .build-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 900; color: var(--gold-bright); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .build-desc {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif; font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--white-dim); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .build-status {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    padding: 4px 14px; animation: pulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    text-align: center; margin-top: 60px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards 1.45s;
  }
  .sigil { font-size: 40px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; opacity: 0.5; }
  .footer-text {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 5px; color: var(--gold-dim); text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
    50%       { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .avatar-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .card-inner { padding: 20px 18px 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scanlines"></div>

<svg class="anubis-deco" width="400" height="700" viewBox="0 0 200 350" fill="#C9A84C">
  <path d="M100 10 C80 10 65 25 60 40 C50 35 35 38 30 50 C25 62 30 75 40 80 C35 90 33 105 38 118 C30 125 25 140 30 155 C35 170 50 175 62 170 L62 220 C55 225 50 235 55 245 C60 255 72 258 80 252 L80 300 C80 310 87 318 97 318 C107 318 113 310 113 300 L113 252 C121 258 133 255 138 245 C143 235 138 225 131 220 L131 170 C143 175 158 170 163 155 C168 140 163 125 155 118 C160 105 158 90 153 80 C163 75 168 62 163 50 C158 38 143 35 133 40 C128 25 113 10 100 10 Z"/>
  <ellipse cx="100" cy="240" rx="15" ry="10" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="4"/>
  <line x1="100" y1="250" x2="100" y2="290" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="4"/>
  <line x1="85" y1="265" x2="115" y2="265" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="4"/>
</svg>

<div class="container">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header class="header">
    <p class="header-eyebrow">Narzędziownik AI · Karta Postaci</p>
    <h1 class="header-title">Anvbis<span>.</span></h1>
    <p class="header-subtitle">nomada <span style="color:var(--gold);opacity:0.6">·</span> cyber assassin <span style="color:var(--gold);opacity:0.6">·</span> psyche lockpick</p>
    <div class="divider">
      <div class="divider-line"></div>
      <span class="divider-symbol">𓂀</span>
      <div class="divider-line right"></div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- 1. AVATAR & INSTALLED -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-stripe"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-label">𓅃 Avatar &amp; Installed</div>
      <div class="avatar-grid">
        <div class="avatar-identity">
          <h2 style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;">
            Avatar Training
            <svg width="52" height="60" viewBox="0 0 80 92" fill="none" style="opacity:0.9;flex-shrink:0">
              <!-- Left ear: sharp triangle -->
              <polygon points="18,44 6,8 32,38" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.8" fill="rgba(201,168,76,0.07)"/>
              <!-- Right ear: sharp triangle -->
              <polygon points="62,44 74,8 48,38" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.8" fill="rgba(201,168,76,0.07)"/>
              <!-- Head circle -->
              <circle cx="40" cy="58" r="28" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.8" fill="rgba(201,168,76,0.04)"/>
              <!-- Nose: small downward triangle -->
              <polygon points="40,70 36,63 44,63" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.4" fill="rgba(201,168,76,0.15)"/>
              <!-- Avatar arrow on forehead: vertical shaft -->
              <line x1="40" y1="30" x2="40" y2="42" stroke="#F2C94C" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <!-- Avatar arrow: horizontal bar -->
              <line x1="33" y1="33" x2="47" y2="33" stroke="#F2C94C" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <!-- Avatar arrow: head pointing down -->
              <path d="M 33 39 L 40 47 L 47 39" stroke="#F2C94C" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="rgba(242,201,76,0.12)"/>
            </svg>
          </h2>
          <p class="role">Level: Magisterka · Build: Egzystencjalna</p>
          <p>Uczę się od różnych plemion, w różnych żywiołach — psychologia, ciało, trening, sztuka, technologia. Bez mapy, bez gotowego przeznaczenia. Metodą prób i doświadczeń.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="avatar-tools">
          <h3>Installed Tools</h3>
          <div class="tool-grid">
            <div class="tool-chip">Claude</div>
            <div class="tool-chip">ChatGPT</div>
            <div class="tool-chip">Gemini</div>
            <div class="tool-chip">Grok</div>
            <div class="tool-chip">NotebookLM</div>
            <div class="tool-chip">Claude Code</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. SKILL TREE -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-stripe"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-label">𓂋 Skill Tree</div>
      <div class="skill-list">
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon">◈</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Pattern Reader</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Obserwacja przyczynowo-skutkowości tam, gdzie jest pozorny chaos.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon">◈</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Deep Diver</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Uważność na to, że każdy temat to bogactwo odnóg, niuansów i tozależyzmów.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon">◈</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Mind-Body Translator</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Wiedza o zależnościach między psychiką i ciałem. Trening duszy na równi z treningiem ciała.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon">◈</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Chaos Navigator</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Rozwijanie ekspertyzy w rozmaitych zakątkach. Może doradzić Ci oczyszczacz powietrza?</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon">◈</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Fake It Architect</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Wejście po omacku i budowanie wiedzy po drodze. Wstępne wymagania tak naprawdę nie istnieją.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. MISSION LOG -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-stripe"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-label">𓆑 Mission Log</div>
      <div class="mission-list">
        <div class="mission-item">
          <span class="mission-num">I.</span>
          <div>
            <div class="mission-text">
              <strong>Zrozumieć siebie</strong>
              Odróżnić to, czego naprawdę chcę, od tego, co powinnam chcieć. Znaleźć powołanie, w które przeleję wiedzę.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-item">
          <span class="mission-num">II.</span>
          <div>
            <div class="mission-text">
              <strong>Aplikacja żywieniowa dla każdego</strong>
              Asystent diety rozumiejący cykl, budżet, alergie i wartości — bo zdrowe odżywianie nie powinno być przywilejem. Pomysł realny. Jeszcze nie zbudowany.
            </div>
            <div class="mission-note">Status: projekt marzeń czekający na właściwy moment</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4. BUGS & BOSSES -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-stripe"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-label">𓂀 Bugs &amp; Bosses</div>
      <div class="bugs-list">
        <div class="bug-item">
          <div class="bug-name">Imposter Protocol</div>
          <div class="bug-desc">„Nic ciekawego nie oferujesz." — głos, który pojawia się dokładnie wtedy, kiedy coś idzie dobrze.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bug-item">
          <div class="bug-name">All-or-Nothing Loop</div>
          <div class="bug-desc">„Albo rzucam wszystko i poświęcam się jednemu, albo nie robię nic." Binarność i bierność tak podobnie brzmią...</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bug-item">
          <div class="bug-name">Worth Equation Error</div>
          <div class="bug-desc">Wartość i ambitność projektu = własna wartość.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5. UNIQUE BOOSTERS -->
  <div class="card booster">
    <div class="card-stripe"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-label">𓆃 Unique Boosters</div>
      <div class="skill-list">
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon" style="color:#4CAF80">⬡</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Podwójny Widok</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Piszesz magisterkę o lęku egzystencjalnym i jednocześnie sama przez to przechodzisz. Perspektywa badaczki i osoby badanej naraz — to rzadkie i cenne.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon" style="color:#4CAF80">⬡</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Random Expertise</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Znasz się na nieprzewidywalnych tematach — pająki, Egipt, pleśń, suplementacja, siłownia. Zgłębiasz wszystko, co Cię zaciekawi lub z czym masz problem.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon" style="color:#4CAF80">⬡</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Ciało Mówi Pierwsze</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Jako trenerka czytasz sygnały ciała zanim głowa zdąży je nazwać. Intuicja somatyczna, której większość ludzi się dopiero uczy.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon" style="color:#4CAF80">⬡</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Shapeshifter</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Płynnie odnajdujesz się w dowolnym kontekście. Dogadujesz się z każdym typem człowieka — nie przez udawanie, ale przez autentyczną ciekawość.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon" style="color:#4CAF80">⬡</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Custom Nano-Detail</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Nie spoczniesz, dopóki nie znajdziesz idealnego, sprawdzonego i dopasowanego rozwiązania. Ubranie, sprzęt, plan treningowy — wszystko musi mieć idealnie szyty sens.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-item">
          <span class="skill-icon" style="color:#4CAF80">⬡</span>
          <div>
            <div class="skill-name">Bullshit Antidotum</div>
            <div class="skill-desc">Szybko i skutecznie filtrujesz fałszywe i tendencyjne informacje. Weryfikujesz w kilku źródłach, rozważasz alternatywne wyjaśnienia — zanim uwierzysz.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 6. DEBUFFS -->
  <div class="card debuff">
    <div class="card-stripe"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-label">𓆙 Debuffs</div>
      <div class="bugs-list">
        <div class="bug-item">
          <div class="bug-name">Identity Fog</div>
          <div class="bug-desc">Trudność zainwestowania skilli w jedno-dwa konkretne drzewka. Wszystko jest interesujące — więc żadne drzewko nie dostaje pełnej mocy.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bug-item">
          <div class="bug-name">Sunk Cost Fear</div>
          <div class="bug-desc">Strach przed zainwestowaniem czasu i serca w coś, z czego „nic nie wyjdzie". Woli nie zaczynać niż stracić.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bug-item">
          <div class="bug-name">It's (not) that Deep</div>
          <div class="bug-desc">Potrzeba dopatrywania się głębszego sensu we wszystkim. Nie robisz rzeczy „ot tak" — każde działanie musi mieć znaczenie. Czasem blokuje, bo nie wszystko wymaga filozoficznej analizy.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 7. ACTIVE BUILD -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-stripe"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-label">𓏏 Active Build</div>
      <div class="build-box">
        <div class="build-title">Karta Postaci AI</div>
        <div class="build-desc">
          Pierwsza rzecz, którą faktycznie puszczam w świat. Nie idealna, nie skończona — ale istniejąca.
          Strona, która mówi: „Jestem tu. Wiem kilka rzeczy. Uczę się reszty."
        </div>
        <div class="build-status">▶ In Progress</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <span class="sigil">𓋹</span>
    <p class="footer-text">Narzędziownik AI · 2025</p>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
